**1. Request Logging**
```dart
Handler middleware(Handler handler) {
  return (context) async {
    print('[${DateTime.now()}] ${context.request.method} ${context.request.uri}');
    final response = await handler(context);
    print('[${DateTime.now()}] Response: ${response.statusCode}');
    return response;
