contentSections.content:
Detect Wasm support before loading your app:

**In JavaScript (index.html):**
```javascript
function supportsWasmGC() {
  try {
    // Check for Wasm GC proposal support
    return typeof WebAssembly.validate === 'function' &&
           WebAssembly.validate(new Uint8Array([
             0x00, 0x61, 0x73, 0x6d, // Wasm magic
             0x01, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, // Version
           ]));
  } catch (e) {
    return false;
  }
}
```

Flutter's loader handles this automatically and falls back to CanvasKit when needed.

